## Hints for Future Agents
- The Codex port uses `~/.cache/codex/repos/<owner>/<repo>/`; do not accidentally revert it to the Claude cache path when syncing with the plugin source.
- The source Claude plugin skill requires `Task(subagent_type=Explore)`, but the Codex port intentionally avoids that hard dependency.
- If updating this port from the Claude plugin later, check for Claude-only frontmatter (`context`, `allowed-tools`), tool names, and cache paths before committing.
- `install.sh` now links both `git-commit` and `repo-explore` into `~/.codex/skills`; newly added skills may still require a new Codex session to appear in available skill metadata.

